_sText:
This map was made by me (fls | nox), to fulfill my dream of seeing the Counter-Strike 1.6 map "awp_map" into Counter-Strike : Source. I really tried to place the things exactly as they were in 1.6, so I hope you guys will enjoy playing it, and for those who played the 1.6 version and already have an idea of how it felt to play it, I hope I won't deceive you ! :D

Have fun ! 

(any comment is appreciated)
